# Terraform Module Manifest
# Resource Group Module

This module is designed to be reusable and follows HashiCorp Terraform best practices.

## Module Metadata
- Name: resource-group
- Version: 1.0
- Provider: azurerm ~> 3.0
- Purpose: Create Azure Resource Groups with consistent tagging

## Usage
source = "./modules/resource-group"

## Files
- main.tf: Azure Resource Group resource definition
- variables.tf: Input variables with validation
- outputs.tf: Exported resource properties
- README.md: Full documentation

## Required Inputs
- resource_group_name: string
- location: string

## Optional Inputs
- tags: map(string)

## Outputs
- resource_group_name: The created resource group name
- resource_group_id: The full resource group ID
- location: The resource group location
- tags: All applied tags
